McCaysville,GA or Copperhill, TN', 'Aska Adventure Area ', '5.5 Miles from Fall Branch Falls ', 'Minutes to Tubing on Toccoa River', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'TreeTops.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-19.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-18.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-2.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-3.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-4.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-5.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-6.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-7.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-8.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-13.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-14.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-15.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-16.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-17.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-10.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-11.jpg', 'Treetops_Pro_2016-12.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Mountain Top Cabin Rentals', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 0.00, '', NULL, '56523');
INSERT INTO `cabinrentals` VALUES (126, 'Aska Adventure Cabin', 'http://ical.liverez.com/fetch/7A594C13-8FA3-4024-9F81-21163EB10A40.ics', NULL, 'Blue Ridge/Aska Area', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Cabin Rental', NULL, NULL, '9', 245.00, NULL, 269.50, 281.75, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Peak Rate ', 'Holiday Rate ', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'We no longer offer a $200 security deposit. Instead, we have a Damage Protection Waiver - \"DPW\" is a $45.00 non-refundable damage waiver that is added to every reservation. The DPF will cover up to $750 in accidental or inadvertent damages if, and only if, the damage/accident is reported at that time of occurrence. This is also listed on the Rental Agreement and FAQ. ', 'Holiday Rates will apply to the following holidays: New Yearâ€™s Holiday, Independence Day Holiday, Thanksgiving Holiday, and Christmas Holiday', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 125.00, NULL, 125.00, NULL, 6, 3, NULL, NULL, 3.0, '3 Kings ', 'Wooded Setting ', NULL, '<p></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\">Looking for adventure?<b> Aska Adventure Cabin</b> is the perfect home base for your excursions in the North Georgia Mountains. You\'ll be minutes from the pristine Toccoa River\'s activities like fishing, tubing, kayaking and a short drive to the scenic hiking trails as you enjoy this well-appointed luxury cabin in a lovely wooded setting.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\">Journey along Aska Road as it chases the Toccoa River and curves through the Blue Ridge Mountains, until you take the paved driveway up the mountainside to this stunning property. Outside, you\'ll see the cozy fire-pit, perfect for those summer nights or cool fall evenings roasting marshmallows or telling tall tales about the Rainbow trout you caught in the near by Toccoa River or the famed Fightingtown or Noontoola Creeks.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\">Inside the main level, industrial meets rustic in the charming, yet posh decor of this cozy, luxe cabin. The kitchen has granite counter tops, custom built rough-sawn cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. You\'ll also enjoy the breakfast bar in the kitchen with three stools for morning coffee or evening cocktails. The dining table seats six comfortably with chairs and bench. The main level stone fireplace has gas logs and features a large TV and surrounded by comfy seating. This level also has a beautiful bath with a gleaming tile and glass shower, granite counter topped vanity that adjoins the main level King size bedroom. This bedroom boasts a large TV as well as door leading to the main level deck. The main level deck has beautiful vintage style cafe string lights that&nbsp; create a gorgeous ambiance in this already lovely space . The main level covered porch also has lots of plush seating, and outdoor dining table, and gas grill.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\">Head up the roughsawn staircase to find the upper level bedroom which features a King size bed, TV, and gorgeous upgraded bathroom with a tile and glass shower &amp; granite bathroom vanity.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\">Head downstairs to enjoy the awesome game room! Here you can find the second gas log fireplace, cozy seating, large TV, pool table, wet bar and third bedroom. The granite counter topped wet bar features lots of&nbsp; prep space for snacks, cocktails and even has a handy mini fridge! The third bedroom has a King size bed, as well as TV and bathroom with shower/tub combo and granite counter topped vanity. Outside this level is the lower deck, but it also features those beautiful lights like the main level, a hand crafted porch swing, outdoor seating plus the relaxing hot tub. After a long day of hiking, exploring, horseback riding the hot tub is great place to recharge under the lovely string lights.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\">All of this located within just 10 minutes of downtown Blue Ridge! Get ready to adventure, relax, and repeat at <b>Aska Adventure Cabin</b>!\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 12px;\">\r\n <br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n <br />Please note: Fireplaces are available for use from October 1st to April 30th. Outdoor WOOD BURNING fireplaces may be used year round, however MTCR does not provide firewood.&nbsp;\r\n <br />Firepits are also available year round but firewood is not provided in firepits. &nbsp;Outdoor gas log fireplaces may not be used out of season.&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Blue Ridge', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Pool Table, Wet Bar, Ping Pong', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=HUYszcKXSSF', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', NULL, 'N', 34.78994800, -84.27137600, NULL, NULL, 47323, 47310, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'linens, dishes, pots, pans, towels, washcloths, etc..', 'Small soaps, initial supply of toilet paper, dishwasher detergent for two cycles, 4 garbage bags for the kitchen.', 'Papertowels, garbage bags(if you will need more than 4) charcoal for grill if needed, starter logs for wood buring fireplaces, washing powders.', NULL, 'Located On Aska Road - Popular for hiking, fishing, tubing, and more!', 'Outdoor Seating ', 'Outdoor Dining ', 'Gas Grill', 'All Granite Countertops', 'Hot Tub', 'Firepit ', 'Gaslog Fireplace (Main Level + Gameroom Level)', 'Luxury Tile Showers (Upper Level + Main Level)', 'Wet bar in gameroom with mini fridge', 'Stainless Steel Applianc