INSERT INTO `cabinrentals` VALUES (142, 'Whispering Water Lodge - NEW!', 'http://ical.liverez.com/fetch/B6ACC80C-9BDB-4B48-B1F0-A940556E017D.ics ', 'JUST ADDED', 'Blue Ridge/Epworth ', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Cabin Rental', NULL, NULL, '4', 995.00, NULL, 1250.00, 1500.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Peak ', 'Holiday ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 325.00, NULL, 8, 4, NULL, NULL, 4.5, 'Four Kings', 'Fightingtown Creek', NULL, '<p> </p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">Experience the true meaning of luxury at Whispering Water Lodge. This next-level property is unmatched and unlike any other... Upon arrival, the impressive architecture of the timber beam entryway with imported Iconic French Quarter-style Gas Copper Lanterns will make jaws drop. As you enter, you will be overwhelmed with beauty, stunning designer decor, custom log and timber craftsmanship, and of course, many stone elements that all flow perfectly together.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">Now, where to even begin? Every room of this property is a masterpiece, and every step is more exciting than the last. The kitchen is a chef\'s paradise with stainless steel Viking appliances, including a gas stove with pot filler, a modern farmhouse-style sink, and endless prep and entertaining space. This is a dream kitchen with its hand-selected Quartz countertops, beautiful cabinetry, and butler\'s pantry just around the corner. This property has four master bedrooms, each unique and stunning. The main level bedroom has a private balcony for two, overlooking the breathtaking estate-like grounds and the roaring Fightingtown Creek frontage. This King Size bedroom has an intimate seating area for two as well, perfect for that morning cup of coffee or pre-dinner cocktails. This room even has an authentic stone wall accent behind the bed. You\'ll see more of this artistic masonry work throughout the property and grounds. Ready to take your breath away again? This bedroom has a full creamy white tile and polished stone bathroom, with a tile shower, soaking tub, and double vanity. Soak in the tub, catching up on those books you\'ve had on your list forever, and enjoy the serenity this dream bathroom brings.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">Wander up the massive log staircase for a view of the top level\'s luxe style amenities and furnishings. The ceiling is designed with custom cut locally milled lumber, sought after by many for its natural blue and gray color variations, making the space pop. The upper-level master suite is quite dreamy and complete with a desk and lounge area with a coffee bar. The bedroom itself is home to a unique private gas fireplace with seating for two, a King size bed, unique tree bark accent wall, TV, private balcony for two overlooking the grounds and water, plus a spacious posh bathroom. The bathroom has a double polished sink vanity on a granite slab, a tile shower with multiple shower heads, and the perfect soaking tub. The lounge area is ideal for enjoying a cup of tea or coffee before you head down to greet your other guests or use the desk to catch up on emails, podcasts, or daily journaling.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">Let\'s explore more: The great room on the main level will wow you again with its soaring ceilings, huge glass windows, stacked stone wall and fireplace, TV, cozy but elegant seating, and sliding glass doors to the most amazing outdoor entertaining area you\'ll ever see! The main level deck has a unique, custom fixture to bring light to the many dinners to be had at the extra-large rough sawn timber beam table. This table was hand-crafted on-site and has two large benches for plenty of space for all your guests. A large, stacked stone wood-burning fireplace welcomes you to enjoy cozy evenings in the comfy outdoor seating. With this luxurious entertaining space, you\'re only limited by your imagination.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">Terrace Level: you\'ll find yet another picture-perfect space: rich, polished floors, a secondary kitchen with stainless steel refrigerator, dishwasher, and plenty of entertaining space on the granite countertops for hors d\'oeuvres or charcuterie and champagne on ice. You\'ll find a 4th fireplace (gas logs) as a welcoming amenity for a warm retreat on chilly nights curled up on the sofa while movie watching and having popcorn or that perfect glass of red wine. This level has two more stunning bedrooms with exquisite designer touches. The bedroom to the left has a King size bed, seating area for two, sliding timber barn doors, and a glass and tile shower with a single polished vanity sink on a granite countertop. The bedroom to the right has a beautiful bathroom as well, with a glass and tile shower plus another polished single vanity on a granite countertop. The bedroom itself has a King size bed, writing desk, and TV.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">Just outside this level is the main event! You\'ll find the hot tub, spacious outdoor seating on the hand-crafted stonemason patio overlooking the incredible creekside setting. Professionally designed landscape and amenities make this stretch of the creek a paradise! A large, crisp putting green doubles as space for cornhole, and a large fire pit with seating creates the perfect place for evenings outside enjoying the rushing creek on these beautiful grounds. Whispering Water Lodge is paradise in many forms, but don\'t forget about the pristine waters just steps from the cabin! Fightingtown Creek is renowned for fishing and is one of the most significant streams home to stocked and wild trout. Not a fisherman? This stretch of creek is one of the most sought-after for the setting itself, ideal for picnics or morning coffee in one of the Adirondack chairs. The water has many spots for wading and enjoying the natural stones and the cool water during warm seasons in the mountains.</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">Whispering Water Lodge is a place you have to see to truly appreciate the exquisiteness of this rare property. Even then, its luxurious beauty is so overwhelming it\'s hard to decide where to begin first. Come explore the enchanting Whispering Water Lodge as it captures your heart and soul. Here, seeing is believing. As Ibn Battuta once said, &ldquo;Traveling &ndash; it leaves you speechless, then turns you into a storyteller.&rdquo; Whispering Water Lodge is where your story begins!</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">Please note: Fireplaces are available for use from October 1st to April 30th. Outdoor WOOD BURNING fireplaces may be used year-round. However, MTCR does not provide firewood.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">Firepits are also available year-round, but firewood is not provided in firepits. Outdoor gas log fireplaces may not be used out of season. </p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Blue Ridge', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Wet Bar, Putting Green & Cornhole', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=4nRVZu4DdBJ', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'N', 'Y', 'N', NULL, 'N', 34.91975300, -84.40908400, NULL, NULL, 10782, 10779, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'linens, dishes, pots, pans, towels, washcloths, etc..', 'Small soaps, initial supply of toilet paper, dishwasher detergent for two cycles, 4 garbage bags for the kitchen.', 'Papertowels, garbage bags(if you will